snippet.title: Crazy Magic: I will guess your age!!!

localized.description:
Crazy! This really works! In this video I will give you some instructions to follow. You will need a calculator (unless you are a maths magic mastermind!) in order to calculate some numbers ... 
Facebook → https://www.facebook.com/dailybroccoli
at the end of which you will indeed end up with your current AGE!

I will guess your age, or even better: Can you guess my age? In any case... believe me: this is a fantastic trick to perform and to leave people puzzled as to your magic powers!
